descript.abstract: This is a graphical polygon dataset depicting the polygon boundaries of the ten City of San Antonio City Council Districts
descript.purpose: The City of San Antonio dataset defines the area of the City Council Districts.
descript.supplinf: According to fields notes the square mile is 466.6. Last official ordinance #2009-06-18-0516
